To avoid the anti-nuclear crowd from swamping our categories I devised separate ones. The ecowackos outnumber us. The World is full of gullible morons unfortunately. If this board gathered a few of these nutcases then they might fill up the board with nonsense. So I created environment as a discussion place for alternative energies and bitching about nuclear power. The idea being that watermelons would be directed to that category for their rubbish posts and not allowed to pollute the serious threads. I should have started a category on Proliferation I guess.<br>
My point is that if we merge boards to include for and against nuclear debate then we might find the board drowning under the weight of anti-nuclear rhetoric. Fine if that's all you ever want to discuss. Not so fine if you like to discuss more. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/bnuclearspace.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hamster>Hamster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>NEP Freighter Crewman</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(8/31/02 3:34:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hijacking of this board.</span><hr size=1> Maybe I'm just blind, but I don't really see that much anti-nuclear sentiment here aside from Yales.  And personally Yales doesn't strike me as your average sloganeering activist that can't discuss their viewpoints outside of emotionalism and political correctness.   With the exception that he tends to get a bit arrogant at times (aren't we all?) I don't think he's really that bad of an influence on the board.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/bnuclearspace.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hamster>Hamster</A> at: 8/31/02 3:36:16 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/uyales.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yales</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 692<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(8/31/02 3:49:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~yales/images/53invad2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hijacking of this board.</spa